zm_labyrinth_map_a1 Map for CSS
---
The map is not standard for Zombie Mod, there are no places on the map where you can sit and fight off zombies. You will have to run through a fairly large maze to escape from zombies. There are 5 items on the map for survivors that they can use (Flamethrower, chainsaw, Pushgun, Speed Weapon, and finally the c4 bomb - it's better to be careful with it)))
---
